data.description: Fabulous Single Story Home with a Very Open Floor Plan in a flourishing family-oriented newer home community. Nearby major arteries and highways to get anywhere you need to go around San Antonio or the Hill Country. The new HEB Grocery Store and FM-211 are now open. You have access to many amenities like a community pool, large park, playground and a huge green space with trails. School children can attend the highly regarded Northside ISD. You will love the layout and comfort in this spacious feeling home inside and out with a high-quality water softener, the covered patio, custom deck and fenced, landscaped yard. The 4th Bedroom is converted to an office with a double-door entry and floor tile.. USDA, FHA, VA Loan eligible. Do not hesitate to go see this very desirable single story home...
